commit_list.message: Added Memcache support, Auth Support Layout is started. Moved from Define for modules to a Loader based system. Now you just have a array of the modules in the settings.inc and do not need to modify the index.php file anymore. the skydas_autoloader() will load anything in the $loaders array with a _loader.php in the lib/loaders folder. This make is so that only index.php changes should only be when enabling core functions. everything should now have a loader,lib and route .php/inc file. Added memcache for the api/queues/all method to hopefully speed up loading and the less calls to esl.
